      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EDDIETEMPLE (3) won a trial back in December before a break and returned with a sneaky trial when tucked in behind horses recently at this track. Pike hops on board for the debut and he looks to have plenty under the bonnet. Can make an immediate impact. ACHY BREAKY (1) resumed with a big win over this track and trip a fortnight ago, lobbing midfield under similar circumstances and proving too good. She meets them worse at the weights, today, but she looks to have good ability and can go on with the job. SUNBLOOD (9) won the trial that EDDIETEMPLE comes through and that holds plenty of weight. She was good in her first trial back this time in also around FARNOVA. Maps to get her chance and a forward showing is expected. FARNOVA (5) set the tempo but couldn't hold off ACHY BREAKY first-up. Better for that effort and can feature in the finish again. CHIXFROMTHESTIX (6) was impressive on debut and can go on with the job.",
